name: WhatIsMyEnergy?
description:
Hi! Today I want to present you my first game "WhatIsMyEnergy"

Control:

WASD - movement;

O - skill tree;

G - dash;

Description:

Try to accumulate as much energy as possible!
Be sure, the Night does not spare anyone!

P.S: "Don't touch the numpad 1, it's only for me!"
